pha_f; the bound is exponential in\nthe number of equations, but we also show that it is essentially optimal.\nConstructing a bound for k_f is still an open problem. Finally, we also provide\na geometric interpretation of Newton's method for SPPs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Jan 2010 17:44:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Jan 2010 11:49:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 16 Mar 2010 16:57:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-03-17"}
