ffusion slope delta, and also on the presence/absence of the local\nunderdensity damping effect on radioactive nuclei. More precise data from\non-going experiments are expected to clarify this issue.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Jan 2010 18:15:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Jul 2010 13:16:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-07-08"}
