d in T .) We also prove a matching lower bound ?(P + A +\n?Ak) on the complexity of exploration for limited vision, even if the terrain\nis known to the robot.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Jan 2010 07:29:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-14"}
